                        <p>The Paragraph elements are used for displaying the
                            content. The ideal standard is no more than 20 words
                            per sentence, five sentences per paragraph. Limit
                            each paragraph to a single idea as it makes it
                            easier to read.</p>

                        <p>Use <kbd>B</kbd> for content which has <strong>strong
